Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be an illustration of text that says 'D.. You feel uninspired as you sit in your cube. A few minutes fjoy watching cat clips on YouTube. When you're colleagues ask a friendly "How do you do?" You simply say "Fine", but you like to say "Blue".'.

Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'You say to yourself, that's the way it must be. There's duties and schedules, and your kid's dentist fees. Ajob is ajob and a job must be done! There's no time to sit around and simply have fun!'.

Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1 So you slumpity- slump your way through each day. And you gripe, and you type, as you labor away. Now, this will not do. No, this simply won t do! Who's running this show, here? It's you, my dear, YOU! ਬaynਣ It's time to start asking what do you want to do?'.

Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Plan some time for yourself, two, three hours day. Leave your smartphone at home out and play. Why have we stopped playing? How silly, how wrong! To think growing up means being earnest all day long.'.

Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be an illustration of text that says 'Remember, you liked to go out and dance? You once played guitar in that weird indie band. Or painting, whatever did happen to that? Strange how all of those passions fell flat.'.

Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Now, ajob is job, and job must be done. But you is you, and you must also have fun. So take week off, one, or two, six, or eight! This is your mental health and that simply can't wait.'.

Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of ‎text that says '‎But wait! It's not easy when money is tight. That's true, but you can still take that art course at night. If risks aren't your thing, work part-time for while. In your new found free time, do things that make you smile. م_د Taking care fyourself is the first job of all. If you don't work at that, soon you'll have no job at all. So, eat grand meal, sing song, learn Malay. Not just once in a while do these things every day.‎'‎.
Photo by War and Peas on July 24, 2021. May be a cartoon of palm trees, sky and text that says 'Yes, job is job and job must be done. But taking care ofyourself, is job Number One. OUT War and Peao'.
